{"tid":692291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［三大御姐系女星］香港有咩御姐級女星？","createTime":"2018-06-06T13:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T05:51:38.000Z","uid":185935,"like":14,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"db6e0bf6401701191e10bc3439f7537d13a595c2","tid":692291,"uid":185935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"老老實實，嚟緊呢個年代一定係御姐系女星玩晒，識食一定食姐姐。<br />\n<br />\n第一，宜家個個都講平權，點解拍拖唔可以女長男幼？<br />\n<br />\n第二，你睇宮心計入面個個唔係人妻就高齡產婦，但紅完未？未喎（留意，御姐系同人妻系係兩回事），根本女人最有魅力就係廿到尾三十先開始。<br />\n<br />\n第三，香港社會後生女上位一定快過男人，同齡女友你點滿足佢？姐姐就唔同，佢唔會期望你養佢，但你可以用你嘅青春令到佢都青春埋，符合市場需求。<br />\n<br />\n但香港要搵高質嘅御姐系女星唔易，唔係人妻就係太淫，再唔係就係扮𡃁妹wtf，要選都唔易<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我先拋磚引肉<br />\n<br />\n李佳芯 Ali （照顧型）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/211845_707e413ba201b61b4f5fc2cbdf463011.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F211845_707e413ba201b61b4f5fc2cbdf463011.png&h=2ceb99af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不用說了吧，人靚，好人，但最緊要係！個樣有少少惡，好想瘋狂俾佢鬧！<br />\n最正係佢宜家紅咗都對男友不離不棄，佢條仔係點我唔理，但做弟弟俾佢照顧實在十分安心呢～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李幸倪 Gin Lee （女強人型）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/211848_d23f647b0e7a062d1a0848aeca4dd4ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F211848_d23f647b0e7a062d1a0848aeca4dd4ec.png&h=febfa66d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/211851_651d72788167b609a7b2eaf8b8b29331.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F211851_651d72788167b609a7b2eaf8b8b29331.png&h=5c982667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/211852_db8f065c781cd452c6ea5bfba3e6bf76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F211852_db8f065c781cd452c6ea5bfba3e6bf76.png&h=622397a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個人嚟香港唱歌浮浮沉沉到宜家上到紅館你就知佢很堅強！唱歌真心好聽，宜家終於小性感（切記！御姐不能太淫），喺屋企等佢呢個女強人返嚟，你係唯一見到佢露出感性嘅一面嘅人，點抗拒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n胡琳 （難以捉摸型）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/211853_db8f065c781cd452c6ea5bfba3e6bf76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F211853_db8f065c781cd452c6ea5bfba3e6bf76.png&h=8a340709&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/211903_9574d6ad28cd9479f6798e68475c4740.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F211903_9574d6ad28cd9479f6798e68475c4740.png&h=61746e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實御姐有個元素好重要，就係「距離」，大部分時間上情感都唔係平等嘅。胡琳的確因為年紀唔細喇，但更重要係嗰種你永遠估唔到佢諗咩嘅感覺，佢未必好叻，未必好強，但感情遊戲你永遠玩唔贏佢咁、但同時永遠有驚喜，乖乖地聽晒佢話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我揀<br />\nGin Lee &gt; Ali &gt; 胡琳<br />\n<br />\n不過香港要搵高質御姐真係唔易，巴打仲有冇"},{"pid":"047186d85a2e1dedc509417bb52dc7c2ed34ca4f","tid":692291,"uid":2419,"like":85,"dislike":2,"score":83,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:36:15.000Z","msg":"汪明荃"},{"pid":"8caf14a1eb60f5e0ae99102c9355d0d6531727ba","tid":692291,"uid":52271,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"鄭裕玲"},{"pid":"7954164970ce819c557874cca0858896a194e9c8","tid":692291,"uid":116530,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"梁舜燕"},{"pid":"2d46f81bb93c1cbd681c8ebe493e08c48ded5a55","tid":692291,"uid":69090,"like":37,"dislike":22,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f100ea0afd457cac1fca0632e9831d71c630e84e","tid":692291,"uid":7206,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"長腳蟹<br />\n王君馨"},{"pid":"25aa01e7e91d7c8db1f1d120a0f0d9cb102bda5c","tid":692291,"uid":185935,"like":18,"disl